test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [-2, -2, -2, -2, -2, -2, ...] == [-2]
  Left contains 9 more items, first extra item: -2
  Full diff:
  - [-2]
  + [-2, -2, -2, -2, -2, -2, -2, -2, -2, -2]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [] == [0]
  Right contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0]
  ?  -
  + []
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [40, 36, 32, 28, 24, 20, ...] == []
  Left contains 10 more items, first extra item: 40
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [40, 36, 32, 28, 24, 20, 16, 12, 8, 4]
